<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK" unique="true">  
    <img planet="PLANET_POPULATED_SMALL"/>
    <text>A small damaged colony lies in the distance. It appears to have once been under Rebel control, but the colonists revolted and broke free. You receive a hail from the colony, marked as urgent.</text>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Respond.</text>
        <event>
            <text>"A Federation ship, here in the Rebel stronghold? Here, before us in our time of most dire need? This truly is our lucky day... As you can see, we have recently broken free from our Rebel oppressor. But it was not without loss. The Rebels took some of us as prisoners and are transporting them back to one of their high security containment facilities. We don't have the manpower to save them, but maybe you can? All you need to do is intercept the jailer ship. We placed a tracking beacon on it before it got away, so finding it won't be difficult."</text> 
            <choice hidden="true">
                <text>Agree to track down the jailer.</text>
                <event>
                    <text>"Oh thank you. I knew we could count on the Federation!"</text>
                    <quest event="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_JAILER"/>
                </event>
            </choice>
            <choice hidden="true">
                <text>We cannot risk our primary mission.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
    <choice hidden="true">
        <text>Avoid the colony.</text>
        <event>
            <text>While it's a relief to see opposition against the Rebel cause even in their territory, you do not have time to stop by and assist with whatever requests these colonists would ask from you.</text> 
            <choice>
                <text>Do something on-board the ship.</text>
                <event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
            </choice>
            <choice>
                <text>Do nothing.</text>
                <event/>
            </choice>
        </event>
    </choice>
</event>
<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_JAILER">
	<text>You've found the Jailer. They're already charging their FTL drive. You'll have to take them down before they can escape, and hopefully not destroy the ship in the process.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_JAILER_PRISONBREAK" hostile="true"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_JAILER_SURRENDER">
	<text>The damaged ship hails you. "Y-you were sent by those colonists weren't you? Fine, you can have the prisoners back. Just let us live."</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Accept the surrender and free the slaves.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The colonists are grateful for your help. As you do not have time to return to the colony, you drop them off at the nearest station, where they will be able to find a ship to help them. You are paid heavily for your assistance.</text>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
			<ship hostile="false"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Screw the mission, let's kill these Rebel bastards.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="DESTROYED_REBEL_PRISONBREAK">
	<text>You've destroyed the jailer, and no doubt all of the colonists onboard. The colony will never give you a reward now, so you'll have to be content with the scrap from the wreckage.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
</event>
<event name="DEAD_CREW_REBEL_PRISONBREAK">
	<text>Without any of the Rebel crew onboard, you're able to scrap the exterior of the ship before checking on the prisoners.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Check on the colonists.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The colonists are grateful for your help. As you do not have time to return to the colony, you drop them off at the nearest station, where they will be able to find a ship to help them. You are paid heavily for your assistance.</text>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_GOTAWAY">
	<text>The Jailer jumps away, and will no doubt arrive at the containment facility before you can catch it. That doesn't mean all hope is lost. You can still track the ship's location, and maybe defeat it before the prisoners are dropped off.</text>
	<quest event="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_FINAL"/>
</event>

<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_FINAL">
	<text>You've tracked down the jailer once again, but they've already transferred crew to a much stronger MFK Ace ship. It won't be an easy fight, and there will be no surrender. If you want to free the colonists, you'll have to kill their crew.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_PRISONBREAK_FINAL" hostile="false"/>
	<customFleet right="true" firing="true" autoDarkening="false">CUSTOM_FLEET_REBEL</customFleet>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Try to rescue the colonists.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Rebels aren't about to back down from a fight. The containment facility activates an ASB satellite to fire upon you.</text>
			<environment type="PDS" target="player"/>
			<ship hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>This is far too dangerous. We should go.</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_FINAL_DEADCREW">
	<text>Without any of the Rebel crew onboard, you're able to scrap the exterior of the ship before checking on the prisoners.</text>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Check on the colonists.</text>
		<event>
			<text>It is very dangerous to transport all of the colonists back to the colony now. With the MFK Ace still intact, most agree to steal the ship and pilot back. However, one colonist decides to stay with you. You are paid for your efforts as well.</text>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
			<crewMember amount="1"/>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="QUEST_REBEL_COLONY_PRISONBREAK_FINAL_DESTROYED">
	<text>You've destroyed the MFK Ace, and likely all of the colonists onboard. You'll have to be content with the salvage the ship provides, and leave quickly before the ASB can destroy you.</text>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
</event>

