<textList name="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_ENGINEER">
	<text>Though the primary Rebel fleet mostly avoids this sector, their Engineer vessels can still be found somewhat frequently. One of these ships has already arrived at this beacon and wastes no time to attack your ship.</text>
	<text>You're hailed by a gruff looking Rebel engineer. "Frankly, I'm not paid enough for this job. Though at the same time, if I kill you maybe I'll get a raise!"</text>
	<text>Only the Rebels could see the opportunity to make their engineer ships just as deadly as their primary fleet. One such ship spots you and attacks!</text>
	<text>A Rebel Engineer ship is exploring this beacon. "Damn it, you should know very well that this sector is off limits!"</text>
	<text>The Rebel Engineers are tasked with repairing damaged Auto-ships in this sector. That doesn't mean they aren't willing to get into a brawl with passing Federation ships. The ship here is evidence of this.</text>
</textList>

