			<ship load="SHIP_ENGINEER_MOTHERSHIP" hostile="false"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>There's time left, swing by and try to salvage some supplies.</text>
				<event>
					<text>As you move in to salvage, you're stopped by a large Engineer vessel. "Damn pirates! We told you to get the hell out of here!" Though the ship moves in to chase you off, you can't help but notice that reactor countdown is still going, and you figure the Engineers must know as well.</text>
