<event name="CYRA_JERRY_SPARE_CREW">
	<text>Cyra's ship is in poor condition, but before you can continue the fight, Jerry pulls you aside. "Please, whatever you do, don't kill Cyra. She can't keep fighting like this for much longer, we can get through this without her dying, as long as you don't finish her off! Please, I know you're a mercenary and a Federation one at that, but there doesn't need to be more bloodshed today!"</text>
