<event name="CYRA_JERRY_SUCCESS">
	<text>You've managed to hold out just long enough, and eventually Cyra's ship comes to a halt. Cyra herself has collapsed, unable to fight any longer, and she reluctantly surrenders.</text>
	<ship hostile="false"/>
	<autoReward level="HIGH">weapon</autoReward>
	<variable name="loc_killedcyra" op="set" val="1"/>
	<choice hidden="true" req="unique_jerry" lvl="1" max_group="0" blue="false">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>With the ship neutralized, you dock at Jerry's request and he rushes aboard to meet Cyra. The wounded Ace is still alive, and with treatment could surely make it out in one piece, but something else is wrong. "I've failed. I had one job, one promise. I'm useless. Jerry... send my regards to Vance..." With that, Cyra draws out her gun, aims it at herself, and pulls the trigger.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event>
					<text>Jerry has no idea what to say. "I... she didn't have to... oh no. I caused all of this. What have I done?"</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Don't blame yourself, kid. Vance would have gotten her anyways.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"What? No! Vance would never have hurt her, especially not with their history. I don't think my uncle even realizes what he's doing. He has a mission, and people go rabid about it. They'll die for him even when he's never asked for it. I need to see him, I'm the only person he'll listen to. I can talk him out of this... make him see the damage he's caused. I'm no good as a fighter, but maybe if you can take me to Node 17, I can put an end to this fighting for good." Jerry looks around him. "As for this ship... well, it's not much use to us anymore. I guess you can take the blueprints. Come on, let's... let's go. I don't want to linger."</text>
							<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_MFK</unlockCustomShip>
							<variable name="ach_crew_jerry" op="set" val="1"/>
						</event>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true" req="unique_jerry" lvl="0" max_group="0" blue="false">
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event>
			<text>"I... I failed... and the kid didn't even survive the fight. What have I done... Damn... damn it all to hell. I'm sorry Vance..." Cyra pulls out her gun, and with trembling fingers aims it at herself and pulls the trigger.</text>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
