	<text>A massive Rebel city has been constructed on the planet below. Somewhat off to the side is a massive villa, with lights so bright it hurts to look at them. Your computer informs you this is the Wentworth Estate. The Vance of this reality doesn't live here in practice of course, but if you had to guess, this is likely where his nephew is residing.</text>
