<event name="JERRY_TAXES" unique="true">
	<text>You notice a small Rebel colony has been constructed nearby. On encrypted channels, they broadcast a simple offer to you, "We know who you are, but times are tough. The Aces here don't follow Cyra's rules anymore, they're taking orders from Universe 1. The taxes are heavy and we'll take any business we can."</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Dock.</text>
		<event load="JERRY_TAXES_DOCK"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Attack them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Of course, the one time we open our arms, and this is how we're treated! Screw the Federation, I'd rather be taxed 'til I'm bankrupt than submit to you tyrants!"</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_STATION" hostile="true"/>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="MORALITY_UPDATE_JERRY_FIGHT"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>No thanks.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Rebels are clearly disappointed, but they say nothing more.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<eventList name="JERRY_TAXES_DOCK">
	<event>
		<text>Fortunately, the Rebels weren't lying, and you're welcomed onboard to trade. However, when an elite vessel, merely the equivalent of a police officer here, comes by and spots you, the Rebels make no attempt to stand by you as the elite makes an arrest!</text>
		<store>STORE_REBEL</store>
		<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_ELITE_FIGHT" hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>Fortunately, the Rebels weren't lying, and you're welcomed onboard to trade. "We just can't stand by the Federation anymore after all they've done, but you're not all bad evidently. I hope you can walk away thinking the same about us."</text>
		<store>STORE_REBEL</store>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
	<event>
		<text>You board the station, only for Rebels to pop out, guns drawn! "Federation filth, we knew you'd fall for this! You break your way into our sector, and we break our way into your FACE! Hahah... eh... that sounded better in my head. Whatever, you're under arrest."</text>
		<ship load="SHIP_REBEL_ELITE_FIGHT" hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Continue...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
	</event>
</eventList>

<event name="JERRY_COLONISTS" unique="true">
	<text>Near the beacon is a large space colony, whose populace is moving about in a busy fashion.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Hail them and ask if they can assist.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Huh? Quit bothering us, Renegade. We're busy gathering our yearly tribute to Jerome. We have to hurry, we can't be late!"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Promise that you'll free them from Jerome's tyranny.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"You'll... what? God damn it, I said leave us alone! We don't have time for this nonsense!" The colony dispatches an Auto-ship to chase you off!</text>
					<ship hostile="true" load="SHIP_AUTO_FIGHT"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Steal the tribute.</text>
				<event load="JERRY_COLONISTS_STEAL"/>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_HUMAN">
				<text>(Human Crew) Have your human pretend to be Rebel personnel and demand supplies.</text>
				<event>
					<text>The colonists sigh. "Sure, for the Rebellion I guess. We'll have a shipment of ammunition and scrap ready for you shortly."</text>
					<autoReward level="MED">missiles</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ignore the colony.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You have no business with these people.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<event name="JERRY_COLONISTS_STEAL">
	<text>The colonists are helpless, and hand over some boxes reluctantly. As you pilot away, you hear them shouting "Damn you, ignorant Federation pig! You're everything wrong with this galaxy! Jerry will show you!"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Open the tribute.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You pry open the boxes, only to find a chocolate cake with 23 unlit candles around it, and a hand-made birthday card. There's nothing in here practical for a military vessel.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="MORALITY_UPDATE_JERRY"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

